description:
This is a PSP only game that can be played using the PPSSPP 0.9.5 emulator.

All other versions didn't emulate this game as well as this one.

This is best played with Xbox360 controller: If you don't have one, I recommend 

buying a generic Xbox360/PC controller from ebay - about $20.


Recommended System Requirements:

Core 2 duo 2.4ghz or higher.

nVidia GeForce GT 610 / ATI Radeon HD 5 series or higher.

2 Gig of ram or more.

Windows XP / Vista / 7 / 8 32 or 64bit OS.



                 Additional info:


Press Alt + Enter to toggle Window Modes.

Press Alt + F4 to end the game.



